=Writing Skills

Here are some materials on scientific writing skills.

- [https://terrytao.wordpress.com/advice-on-writing-papers/ On writing], a blog of [https://www.math.ucla.edu/~tao/ Terence Tao].

- [http://www.mit.edu/~dimitrib/Ten_Rules.html Ten simple rules for mathematical writing] given by [http://www.mit.edu/~dimitrib/home.html Dimitri P. Bertsekas].

See also the [http://www.dcsc.tudelft.nl/~mohajerin/writing.html scientific writing] page owned by [http://www.dcsc.tudelft.nl/~mohajerin/index.html Peyman Mohajerin Esfahani].
